            We want you to be safe and well-informed as you participate in online programs!
          </p>

          <p>
            <%= link_to "Internet Safety Training",
              "http://iridescentlearning.org/internet-safety/",
              target: "_blank" %>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="tab-content" id="your-account">
      <%= render 'student/dashboards/full_access_content/account' %>
    </div>
  </div>
